                if j in (3, 4, 5):                           # AUM Total / Perú / Cubierto
                    c.number_format = FMT_S
                elif j == 6:                                 # % ponderación
                    c.number_format = FMT_P
                elif 8 <= j <= 17:                           # bloques % / monto por nivel
                    c.number_format = FMT_P if (j % 2 == 0) else FMT_S
                elif 18 <= j <= 21:                          # scores
                    c.number_format = FMT_SC; c.fill = fill_score(v)
                elif j == 22 and fill_mit(v):                # mitigante
                    c.fill = fill_mit(v)
                elif j == 24:                                # Cobertura CENEPRED (%)
                    c.number_format = FMT_P; c.alignment = A_C
                elif j in (25, 26):                          # Activos totales / sin cobertura
                    c.number_format = '#,##0'; c.alignment = A_C
```

Nota: los bloques de nivel ahora arrancan en col 8 y el `%` cae en columnas **pares** (`j % 2 == 0`).

